ImThreshold.
Linux fork BookScanLib.ru (http://djvu-soft.narod.ru/bookscanlib/).
It's a set of command line tools to create color images of djvu.

 Make DjVu:

  imthreshold-a4
  imthreshold-anytodjvu
  imthreshold-anytominidjvu

 Threshold:

  imthreshold-tdalg
  imthreshold-tdjvul
  imthreshold-tgatos
  imthreshold-tglobal
  imthreshold-thalftone2
  imthreshold-tlocal
  imthreshold-ttext
  imthreshold-twhiterohrer

 Filters:

  imthreshold-fautoinv
  imthreshold-fdespeckle
  imthreshold-filter
  imthreshold-finfo
  imthreshold-fpmean

 Scale:

  imthreshold-sbwmag2
  imthreshold-scris
  imthreshold-shris
  imthreshold-size

 Other:

  imthreshold-deskew
  imthreshold-rotate
  imthreshold-separate
  imthreshold-tlayer
  imthreshold-math
  imthreshold-bash-scripts

